{"tid":57594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好人好姐真係唔好同港女玩","createTime":"2016-12-28T06:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T05:05:56.000Z","uid":50286,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e94dd5365dee759918ade062545d49403a93c7","tid":57594,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n<br />\n個港女同事都痴痴地線，<br />\n<br />\n開頭以為個死八婆judy鐘意我啦成日約我食晏，<br />\n<br />\n點知原來呃飯食利用我依d小毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日去到間餐廳就話唔記得帶銀包，佢生日，我生日又係我請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他同事仲以為我同佢拍拖啦，佢即刻急急腳澄清仲話我唔係佢條仔但係對佢好過條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我又蠢唔曬既，今日專登唔帶銀包同佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我仲嗌多左份牛河拎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到埋單個陣好有霸氣咁同佢講：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝曬你餐飯呀JUDY姐</span></span><br />\n<br />\n頭也不回就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打請問我點樣可以呃返幾餐飯食填返下面條數？<br />\n<br />\n乾炒牛河 $31 加凍檸茶$4 = $35<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞$24蚊餐（麥當勞都要我請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n辛辣地獄拉麵$118<br />\n<br />\n唔知咩水餃餐$39<br />\n<br />\n5 course indian set lunch $58"},{"pid":"63518ecb7e2bd20b832003be88e255e1909422f3","tid":57594,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比港女呃錢"},{"pid":"be206db121b5c56cc1885c72feda6ab10a64100e","tid":57594,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"點解唔同我玩😭"},{"pid":"627aaea79f2e81b9b42eea6b45ecbb98d6662262","tid":57594,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔同我玩😭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呃錢"},{"pid":"e36336ce21b09e1da6097bfce93e1d01874b581b","tid":57594,"uid":37245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:48:42.000Z","msg":"「細過夠話唔同女仔玩啦；所以大個咪比女仔玩囉」 黃子華"},{"pid":"b1d28422bdda79d6f81da165fcd34e5bbdf3206f","tid":57594,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「細過夠話唔同女仔玩啦；所以大個咪比女仔玩囉」 黃子華</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比返d lunch錢我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc2bd0d42ea728578e9619498dea6aed4a9ecca","tid":57594,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打同我一樣比港女呃過錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1531639883535f8d78000dea26af9f64e1cf7b3d","tid":57594,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T09:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b7323d8bd6ddacf53e091cab745ea5ac7819c5","tid":57594,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20